 # Cloudflare Pages security headers — applied to every route.
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
#
# ── Notes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HSTS: max-age is 1 year with includeSubDomains. NO "preload" token — that
#   one is near-permanent (removal requires submitting to the browser
#   preload list and waiting months). Add it only if you're 100% committed
#   to HTTPS-only forever. To back out of HSTS, lower max-age (e.g. =0);
#   browsers drop the policy on their next visit.
#
# CSP: script-src pins the inline <script> blocks by SHA-256 hash (four
#   unique hashes: the theme bootstrap shared by all three pages, the main
#   IIFE in index.html, the IIFE in 404.html, and the year line in
#   impressum.html), so no 'unsafe-inline' is needed for scripts. IF YOU
#   EDIT ANY INLINE SCRIPT the page's JS will be blocked until you
#   regenerate its hash. Regenerate:
#
#     python3 - <<'PY'
#     import re,hashlib,base64
#     for f in ["index.html","impressum.html","404.html"]:
#         h=open(f,encoding="utf-8").read()
#         for m in re.finditer(r'<script([^>]*)>(.*?)</script>',h,re.S):
#             if "src=" in m.group(1) or "ld+json" in m.group(1): continue
#             print(f, "'sha256-"+base64.b64encode(
#                 hashlib.sha256(m.group(2).encode()).digest()).decode()+"'")
#     PY
#
#   style-src keeps 'unsafe-inline' (the inlined <style> blocks are large and
#   change often; hashing them is brittle and style injection is low-risk).
#   static.cloudflareinsights.com / cloudflareinsights.com are required by
#   Cloudflare Web Analytics (auto-injected) — removing them breaks analytics.
#
# To roll back CSP safely: rename the header to
#   Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only
# It then only logs violations to the browser console instead of blocking.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), camera=(), display-capture=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=(), browsing-topics=()
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'; form-action 'self'; img-src 'self'; font-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; script-src 'self' 'sha256-5z4n/JiPuEt+6mQbIO7TVk4vQE+MPbwAxqgF1ZjHG1s=' 'sha256-oCukgEyMIKbtVie0L0jBbpwULLyBOFGb9Gu/tWjcD8w=' 'sha256-P6VhVxRwM9KXfb+I+jQV1R0ubd6GproPXbKNYc5fzmg=' 'sha256-VO4XPK9S020sabWP72Ql+pf7mcl8XoZqNJt7zSWaKmk=' https://static.cloudflareinsights.com; connect-src 'self' https://cloudflareinsights.com; upgrade-insecure-requests
